<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4754933>
    dc:description "Figs 13–27: Tergite and sternite of the male genital segment and aedeagus of Pachycorynus lanceolatus spec. nov. (13–15), Metolinis vucanalis spec. nov. (16–18), Metolinis jubing spec. nov. (19–21) (scale bar: 0.1 mm), Phacophallus philippinus spec. nov. (22–24), and Medhiama nepalica spec. nov. (25–27) (scale bar: 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4754933/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

